  - elementId: insight-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [880, 384, 330, 270]
    content:
      fontSize: 13
      color: "$text"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p><span style="font-size:13px; color:#ffffff;"><strong>1. 收入端</strong></span></p>
        <p><span style="font-size:12px; color:#C0C0C0;">核心业务增长22%，新业务贡献收入占比提升至18%，海外市场收入同比增长67%</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="font-size:13px; color:#ffffff;"><strong>2. 成本端</strong></span></p>
        <p><span style="font-size:12px; color:#C0C0C0;">规模效应显现，单位成本下降8.5%；供应链优化节省成本约¥12亿</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="font-size:13px; color:#ffffff;"><strong>3. 前瞻指引</strong></span></p>
        <p><span style="font-size:12px; color:#C0C0C0;">管理层上调全年收入指引至¥950-980亿，净利率目标30%+</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="font-size:13px; color:#E8B931;"><strong>评级：强烈推荐 | 目标价上调15%</strong></span></p>

  # 底部darkpanel footer
